  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_139",
    "english": "Demon, a member of the onis. They can usually be seen in places with a strong demonic presence. Their physical features are their size, much larger than a human, and their two pairs of arms. Holding a giant axe in one hand, whereas a human would need two hands, they cut every enemy in half.",
